cat << EOF
MIME-Lite is intended as a simple, standalone module for generating MIME
messages... specifically, it allows you to output a simple, decent
single- or multi-part message with text or binary attachments.  It does not
require that you have the Mail:: or MIME:: modules installed.
EOF
